import login from "../Icons/login.png";
import {
  Image,
  Breadcrumb,
  BreadcrumbItem,
  BreadcrumbLink,
  Flex,
} from "@chakra-ui/react";
export default function Tabs() {
  return (
    <Flex
      position="absolute"
      top="13vh"
      right="5vw"
      fontFamily="GenSenRounded"
      alignItems="center"
      fontSize="larger"
      color="#928c71"
      fontWeight="bold"
    >
      <Breadcrumb>
        <BreadcrumbItem>
          <BreadcrumbLink href="/introduciton">關於我們</BreadcrumbLink>
        </BreadcrumbItem>
        <BreadcrumbItem>
          <BreadcrumbLink href="/">最新消息</BreadcrumbLink>
        </BreadcrumbItem>
        <BreadcrumbItem>
          <BreadcrumbLink href="/">甜點課程</BreadcrumbLink>
        </BreadcrumbItem>
        <BreadcrumbItem>
          <BreadcrumbLink href="/">烘焙環境</BreadcrumbLink>
        </BreadcrumbItem>
        <BreadcrumbItem>
          <BreadcrumbLink href="/">聯絡我們</BreadcrumbLink>
        </BreadcrumbItem>
      </Breadcrumb>
      {/* <Button>關於我們</Button>
      <Button>最新消息</Button>
      <Button>甜點課程</Button>
      <Button>烘焙環境</Button>
      <Button>聯絡我們</Button> */}
      <Image src={login} w="30px" ml="30px" />
    </Flex>
  );
}
